{"title": "Booth", "summary": "Lighting Show", "body": "This Booth was developed for a lighting show in New York. It uses transparency and cutout to pique the curiosity to what is inside. Luminaires flow through the structure and are allowed to exceed its limits. The booth is also used as the crate itself.\n\n*2022*\n\n[lp=Booth (3).jpg]\n\n\n**&&Shipping & Installation&&**\n\nThe booth is delivered closed with particle boards screwed in to protect it. In the installation, the structure separates in half diagonally and beams are screwed on top to form a pergola.\n\n[lp=Booth (4).jpg]\n\n**&&Details&&**\n\n[lp=Booth (2).jpg]\n[lp=Booth (1).jpg]\n[lp=Booth (5).jpg]", "image": "Booth (3).jpg", "id": 16}